verbose_text: These included : SH2B3 and Ataxin2 (ATXN2), associated with spinocerebellar ataxia 2 53 on chromosome 12; autophagy / beclin-1 regulator 1 (AMBRA1), important in autophagy and the development of the nervous system 54 on chromosome 11; diacylglycerol kinase, zeta (DGKZ), involved in intracellular signalling, 55 on chromosome 5; and neuron navigator 1 (NAV1), expressed in the nervous system and thought to have a role in neuronal development and regeneration, 56 on chromosome 1.
